description: The Gibson Les Paul is an icon that has graced the world's stages and studios for over 60 years.
The Gibson ES-335 is quite possibly the world's most versatile guitar.
The Telecaster is for all intents and purposes the first commercially successful solidbody electric guitar.
The Fender Stratocaster is the instrument used by Jimi Hendrix, Richie Blackmore, Eric Clapton and John Mayer.
